---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="關於 Taiwan.md" description="Taiwan.md 是開源、AI-friendly 的台灣知識庫">
  <div class="about-page">
    <div class="container">
      <header class="page-header">
        <h1>關於 Taiwan.md</h1>
        <p class="lead">開源、AI-friendly 的台灣完整知識庫</p>
      </header>

      <section class="about-content">
        <div class="grid">
          <div class="content-main">
            <h2>我們的願景</h2>
            <p>
              Taiwan.md 致力於打造最完整、最準確、最易於理解的台灣知識庫。
              我們相信，透過開放且結構化的方式分享知識，能夠促進對台灣的深度理解，
              並讓全世界都能認識真正的台灣。
            </p>

            <h2>為什麼選擇 Taiwan.md？</h2>
            <ul class="features-list">
              <li>
                <strong>策展式內容：</strong> 不是百科全書的堆疊，而是經過精心策展的深度內容
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>AI-Friendly：</strong> 結構化的內容設計，讓 AI 也能理解和傳播台灣文化
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>多層次閱讀：</strong> 30秒概覽 → 5分鐘深入 → 完整探索，適合不同需求
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>開源協作：</strong> 社群驅動，持續更新，確保內容的準確性與時效性
              </li>
            </ul>

            <h2>內容範圍</h2>
            <p>
              Taiwan.md 涵蓋台灣的 12 個主要面向，從歷史文化到當代生活，
              從自然地理到科技發展，呈現台灣的完整面貌。
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="sidebar">
            <div class="stats-card">
              <h3>專案統計</h3>
              <div class="stat">
                <div class="stat-number">12+</div>
                <div class="stat-label">主要面向</div>
              </div>
              <div class="stat">
                <div class="stat-number">100+</div>
                <div class="stat-label">預計文章</div>
              </div>
              <div class="stat">
                <div class="stat-number">雙語</div>
                <div class="stat-label">中英對照</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="contribute-card">
              <h3>參與貢獻</h3>
              <p>
                Taiwan.md 是社群驅動的開源專案，歡迎所有對台灣有興趣的朋友參與貢獻。
              </p>
              <div class="cta-buttons">
                <a href="/contributing" class="btn btn-primary">貢獻指南</a>
                <a href="https://github.com/frank890417/taiwan-md" target="_blank" class="btn btn-secondary">
                  GitHub
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .page-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1f2937;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: #6b7280;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .about-content {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .content-main {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #374151;
  }

  .content-main h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1f2937;
    margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem 0;
  }

  .content-main h2:first-of-type {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .content-main p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .features-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .features-list li {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .features-list li::before {
    content: "✓";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #059669;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .sidebar {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .stats-card,
  .contribute-card {
    background: #f9fafb;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
  }

  .stats-card h3,
  .contribute-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1f2937;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .stat {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .stat:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #1e40af;
    display: block;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #6b7280;
  }

  .contribute-card p {
    color: #6b7280;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .btn {
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: #1e40af;
    color: white;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #1d4ed8;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: white;
    color: #1e40af;
    border: 2px solid #1e40af;
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: #1e40af;
    color: white;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-header h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .sidebar {
      order: -1;
    }

    .cta-buttons {
      flex-direction: row;
    }
  }
</style>